snippet.textDisplay: If one is going to audition for AI, The Voice, or any other singing COMPETITION, then he or she must be well-rounded in music. The thing is, AI has been on for YEARS! We all know how it works! We all know sometimes the songs are chosen for the contestants, and the songs may not fit the contestants’ genres. This is like going for a job interview. Know the company’s guidelines and structure before diving in. The show could have placed the partners together by their specific genres, but this responsibility was placed on the contestants. In real life, singers choose their duet partners. AI is doing a great job at showing the contestants how the music industry works!
